Recommends: libnotify-bin
Description: Voice-to-text daemon for Linux using OpenAI Whisper
 Papagaio is a voice input daemon that runs as a background service
 and transcribes speech to text using OpenAI's Whisper model.
 .
 Self-contained binary. No Python runtime required.
 .
 Features:
  * Global hotkey (Ctrl+Alt+V by default)
  * 100% local processing (privacy-first)
  * Voice Activity Detection (VAD) with auto-stop
  * Manual stop and cancel support
  * Bilingual interface (English/Portuguese)
  * Systemd user service with auto-start
